{"tid":662151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片： 大銀幕被扑爆　車主：差人叫我查案","createTime":"2018-05-12T07:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T11:35:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7977b3b99e4b58ed1571c1863a9075154220a138","tid":662151,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T07:35:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180512/20388527?_ga=2.191993634.96320611.1526110183-581282530.1504247435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180512%2F20388527%3F_ga%3D2.191993634.96320611.1526110183-581282530.1504247435&d=JjlPAKBfLcjFdlmPxKK6DP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=c968629f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180512%2F20388527%3F_ga%3D2.191993634.96320611.1526110183-581282530.1504247435&h=ff9f5214\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180512/20388527?_ga=2.191993634.96320611.1526110183-581282530.1504247435</a><br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：<br />\n大銀幕被扑爆　車主：差人叫我查案<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180512/large/a1406a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180512%2Flarge%2Fa1406a.gif&h=29b06d8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■街坊Look男人（左圖）執起嚿石掟爆大銀幕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n村地泊車箒，咩事會得罪人俾人扑車呢？從事裝修工程的鄧先生表示，之前喺西貢斬竹灣接咗單Job，喺嗰度做裝修，為咗方便往返，他揸Audi房車出入，將車泊喺村口空地，「問過村民，話唔阻路唔阻人，冇乜所謂。」泊咗大約半年都相安無事，點知到本周三就出事啦。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泊村地出事<br />\n<br />\n話說鄧先生當日早上如常開車到空地泊車，至傍晚6點幾取車時，見到架車成塊大銀幕爆晒，呈蜘蛛網狀裂紋，於是翻睇車cam還原事發經過，發現有個着短衫褲街坊Look男人從橫巷走出來，不分由說喺草叢執起嚿石頭掟爆大銀幕，之後不知所終。鄧先生稱按疑兇衣着，應該係住附近的村民，但對事件起因一頭霧水，「噚日泊位冇阻路，仲夠一架中型貨車過，之前又冇同人嘈，點解俾人掟石，諗極唔明。」<br />\n<br />\n最令他激氣的是，他立刻報警，差人回應話嗰度係私家路，冇人手長期擺喺度幫手查案，「叫我提供多啲線索，話見到佢一係報警，一係捉住佢再報警，或者靜靜哋跟住佢睇佢入邊間屋。」佢話唔知差人係咪有心做單案。警方則回應案件已列刑事毀壞，正追查逞兇者下落。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180512/large/a1406b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180512%2Flarge%2Fa1406b.gif&h=a73f6a69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：工會促運輸署准車廂裝cam自保<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n今日焦點●即聽"},{"pid":"ae7b57aba4748046ad02642e00d5a3795b91f2da","tid":662151,"uid":63202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T07:36:57.000Z","msg":"牛屎佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3ceeb7cbbdb3a881d08d50d1eb0a46f03ff772","tid":662151,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T07:41:02.000Z","msg":"再嘈放你石墩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a18626ae079e4e1e7d8fb0da5d75b356d11fb63","tid":662151,"uid":5489,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T07:46:32.000Z","msg":"「差人回應話嗰度係私家路，冇人手長期擺喺度幫手查案」<br />\n乜撚野理由黎<br />\n屌你老母黑警 唔知仲以為講緊賭王陳金城係公海殺人單案"},{"pid":"b63544f14f7bf9ac93af3113c62cbc6a705ae550","tid":662151,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T07:50:28.000Z","msg":"只有果條路嘅註冊人有權拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba64c7e31594a3cda4e58515892c78648b8165bb","tid":662151,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T07:53:07.000Z","msg":"廢警"},{"pid":"fa2e80929cbb20ab2fac13328fb3c02162e8a2a2","tid":662151,"uid":92353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T07:54:30.000Z","msg":"如果舊石上面寫住香港獨立可能極速破案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f596fcc2bc45f071b7a5e4c35f3d3f1e26ae487a","tid":662151,"uid":5489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b63544f14f7bf9ac93af3113c62cbc6a705ae550","tid":662151,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim